#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.transpose.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.tensor.transpose"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.misc.transpose.transpose:1 of
msgid "Returns an array with axes transposed."
msgstr "返回一个轴被转置的数组。"

#: maxframe.tensor.misc.transpose.transpose:3 of
msgid ""
"For a 1-D array, this returns an unchanged view of the original array, as"
" a transposed vector is simply the same vector. To convert a 1-D array "
"into a 2-D column vector, an additional dimension must be added, e.g., "
"``mt.atleast_2d(a).T`` achieves this, as does ``a[:, mt.newaxis]``. For a"
" 2-D array, this is the standard matrix transpose. For an n-D array, if "
"axes are given, their order indicates how the axes are permuted (see "
"Examples). If axes are not provided, then ``transpose(a).shape == "
"a.shape[::-1]``."
msgstr ""
"对于一维数组，这将返回原始数组的一个未更改视图，因为转置向量就是相同的"
"向量。要将一维数组转换为二维列向量，必须添加一个额外的维度，例如 ``mt."
"atleast_2d(a).T`` 可以实现这一点，``a[:, mt.newaxis]`` 也可以。对于二维"
"数组，这是标准的矩阵转置。对于 n 维数组，如果指定了轴，则它们的顺序表示轴"
"如何进行置换（参见示例）。如果没有提供轴，则 ``transpose(a).shape == a."
"shape[::-1]``。"

#: maxframe.tensor.misc.transpose.transpose of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.misc.transpose.transpose:13 of
msgid "Input array."
msgstr "输入数组。"

#: maxframe.tensor.misc.transpose.transpose:15 of
msgid ""
"If specified, it must be a tuple or list which contains a permutation of "
"[0,1,...,N-1] where N is the number of axes of `a`. The `i`'th axis of "
"the returned array will correspond to the axis numbered ``axes[i]`` of "
"the input. If not specified, defaults to ``range(a.ndim)[::-1]``, which "
"reverses the order of the axes."
msgstr ""
"如果指定，则它必须是一个包含 [0,1,...,N-1] 排列的元组或列表，其中 N 是 `a"
"` 的轴数。返回数组的第 `i` 个轴对应于输入中编号为 ``axes[i]`` 的轴。如果"
"未指定，默认为 ``range(a.ndim)[::-1]``，即轴顺序反转。"

#: maxframe.tensor.misc.transpose.transpose of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.misc.transpose.transpose:22 of
msgid "**p** -- `a` with its axes permuted. A view is returned whenever possible."
msgstr "**p** -- 轴被置换后的 `a`。只要可能，返回的是视图。"

#: maxframe.tensor.misc.transpose.transpose of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.misc.transpose.transpose:26 of
msgid "备注"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.misc.transpose.transpose:27 of
msgid ""
"Use ``transpose(a, argsort(axes))`` to invert the transposition of "
"tensors when using the `axes` keyword argument."
msgstr ""
"在使用 `axes` 关键字参数时，可以使用 ``transpose(a, argsort(axes))`` 来"
"逆转张量的转置。"

